      <title>私人监狱运营商 Geo 利用贷款市场进行再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/private-prison-operator-geo-taps-loan-market-in-refinancing-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私人监狱运营商 Geo Group Inc. 正在进军债务市场，包括出售一笔 4 亿美元的杠杆贷款，这是一项再融资举措，其竞争对手几周前也采取了同样的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/private-prison-operator-geo-taps-loan-market-in-refinancing-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 13:23:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
