    <item>
      <title>尽管成本上涨，澳大利亚房价仍继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/australia-s-home-prices-extend-gains-even-as-elevated-costs-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于负担能力下降和借贷成本达到 12 年来的高点，澳大利亚房地产市场 3 月份连续第 14 个月上涨，这使得该国两个最大城市的势头降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/australia-s-home-prices-extend-gains-even-as-elevated-costs-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 13:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
